// ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// Kiro niri baseline config  (config.kdl)
// ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// Target: niri (scrollable-tiling Wayland compositor). Config format: KDL.
// Lives at: ~/.config/niri/config.kdl
//
// Desktop shell: noctalia-shell (Quickshell v4) — provides the bar, launcher,
// lock screen, notifications, wallpaper, control center, session menu and
// polkit agent. niri is only the compositor; everything else is noctalia,
// driven over `qs -c noctalia-shell ipc call <module> <action>`.
//
// Modular: each concern lives in its own cfg/*.kdl file, pulled in below.
// Modeled on CachyOS's niri+noctalia settings, carrying Kiro's SUPER-based
// keybind philosophy and app defaults.
//
// Docs: https://github.com/YaLTeR/niri/wiki/Configuration:-Introduction
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

include "./cfg/animation.kdl"
include "./cfg/autostart.kdl"
include "./cfg/keybinds.kdl"
include "./cfg/input.kdl"
include "./cfg/display.kdl"
include "./cfg/layout.kdl"
include "./cfg/rules.kdl"
include "./cfg/misc.kdl"
